American actor, film director, and political activist, Danny Glover will be the guest speaker at the gala dinner of the 10th National Congress of the National Union of Metalworkers of South Africa (Numsa), taking place in Cape Town. Numsa acting spokesperson Patrick Craven said that Glover, a friend of Numsa , would address the dinner at the Cape Town International Convention Centre on Thursday evening. African News Agency For more news your way, follow The Citizen on Facebook and Twitter.